{
  "stem": "1929.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 470.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were disembarked from the train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was really happy to-- to be there, because they deloused us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had showers and some chemical-- DT and T, or some-- and I felt clean.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "For the first time in many years, I felt clean.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they gave us these flannel, little uniforms.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So in that way, I was pleased that I was there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the place was, after being in Tschenstochau, which was such a shambles, this was an organized place.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they took us to a barrack, and-- and--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was-- the whole internal organization was the inmates.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were prisoners there, political prisoners.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Some were German.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Some were from Belgium and other countries.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a huge place, over 100,000 people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was jam packed, because there were-- see, at that time, all the Polish camps had been overrun.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So they didn't have that many facilities.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they jammed prisoners into-- prisoners?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I wasn't a prisoner.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But they jammed us into Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So it was very jam packed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were in-- I was in a barrack.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we slept, like, you know, 20, 30-- it was just one big board every few feet.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And people slept.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you woke up in the morning, and there were one or two bodies that were dead.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in the morning, this detail would come in, of inmates.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They would take all the dead bodies and take them to the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And things were--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was there strictly by myself.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I had no idea what happened to my brother or my father.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I didn't like it one bit to be there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was very tough.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We had to stay on-- in this cold weather, you had to stay.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
